title: Sahl سهل

creator: EgyptPay
descriptionHtml:
Sahl is the only mobile app in Egypt that allows you to charge your electricity card directly from your phone.

20+ PAYMENT SERVICES

- Electricity card charge (Globaltronics & Sewedy Electrometer users)
- Electricity bill payment (All electricity distribution companies)
- Water bill payment (Cairo Water, Alexandria Water)
- Gas bill payment (Petrotrade)
- Mobile line top-up and bill payment (Vodafone, Orange, Etisalat & WE)
- Landline bill payment (WE)
- ADSL top-up and bill payment (WE)
- Donations (Baheya, Magdy Yakoub & many more)
- TV subscriptions (BEIN)

SAFE PAYMENT CHANNELS

Safely save your card information and pay through our app as we are PCI compliant.


VARIOUS PAYMENT METHODS

Choose your preferred payment method. (Bank Card, Meeza Card or any digital wallet)


TRACK ELECTRICITY CARD CONSUMPTION

Access your prepaid electricity meter's data and track your consumption trends.


TRACK PAYMENT HISTORY

All your payment receipts are saved in your payment history for you to view, compare and manage your payment trends.



Contact us at support@sahlpay.app or 01206799994 to exchange your Globaltronics electricity card with an NFC-enabled card to start using the application right away.

descriptionHtml:
A simple and secure way to manage, track, and pay your bills, all in one place.

Hassle-free electricity payment. The only mobile app in Egypt that allows you to charge your electricity card directly from your phone.

20+ PAYMENT SERVICES

- Electricity Card Charge
- Electricity Bill Payment
- Water Bill Payment (Cairo Water, Alexandria Water)
- Gas Bill Payment (Petrotrade)
- Mobile Line Top-Up and Bill Payment(Vodafone, Orange, Etisalat & WE)
- Landline Bill Payment (WE)
- ADSL Top-Up and Bill Payment (WE)
- TV Subscriptions (BEIN)
- Donations
- Education (Cairo University, Ain Shams University, Helwan University, Alexandria University,...etc)
- Game Vouchers (PS, PUBG)


•MANAGE ALL YOUR PAYMENTS/BILLS
A wide range of services, and subscriptions at your disposal.

•TRUST SAHL SECURE TRANSACTIONS
Safely save your card information and pay through our app as we are PCI compliant.

•ENJOY VARIOUS PAYMENT METHODS
Choose your preferred payment method. (Bank Card, Meeza Card or any digital wallet)

•TRACK ELECTRICITY CARD CONSUMPTION
Access your prepaid electricity meter's data and track your consumption trends.

•TRACK PAYMENT HISTORY
All your payment receipts are saved in your payment history for you to view, compare and manage your payment trends.


Get your NFC-enabled card:
Contact us at support@sahlpay.app or 0235372501 to exchange your Globaltronics electricity card with an NFC-enabled card to start using the application right away.

Get in Touch:
Find us on Facebook or Instagram @sahlpayapp
